
1. Install xcode tools (necessary only for the command line's tools)
  xcode-select --install

2. Install Brew (Mac OS package manager)
  /usr/bin/ruby -e "$(curl -fsSL https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Homebrew/install/master/install)"
  brew update

3. Instal iTerm (https://www.iterm2.com/)
  brew cask install iterm2  
  
4. Instal bash ($oh my zsh!) via curl
  sh -c "$(curl -fsSL https://raw.github.com/robbyrussell/oh-my-zsh/master/tools/install.sh)"

5. Virtual machine (to have a separate environment for each projectP)
  - Vagrant
  - Virtual Box

6. Install git (via brew)
  brew install git

7. Extras and unnecesary
  - brew install fortune (quotes in terminal)
  - brew install cowsay (quotes in terminal)
